So she adds extra meat to your meals.

29
00:02:40,793 --> 00:02:42,632
Now is the crucial moment.

30
00:02:42,873 --> 00:02:44,233
Just hang in there for two more days

31
00:02:44,392 --> 00:02:46,593
and reap the benefits.

32
00:02:47,233 --> 00:02:48,433
It doesn't matter if you've covered

33
