You happen to be in charge
of taking out the trash every day.

50
00:04:01,953 --> 00:04:04,153
Help me take something out.

51
00:04:04,233 --> 00:04:05,112
If it succeeds,

52
00:04:05,912 --> 00:04:09,313
not only you, but everyone here
will be able to escape.

53
00:04:14,353 --> 00:04:15,513
Are you serious?

54
00:04:21,193 --> 00:04:21,633
Okay.

55
00:04:22,272 --> 00:04:23,352
Give it to me.

56
00:04:24,473 --> 00:04:25,873
I'll take it out for you.

57
00:04:33,112 --> 00:04:36,272
Or we can discuss it later after work.

58
00:04:36,993 --> 00:04:37,552
Okay.

59
00:04:59,832 --> 00:05:03,352
I apologize for last night.

60
00:05:03,913 --> 00:05:05,993
I was only concerned about myself

61
00:05:06,512 --> 00:05:07,792
and didn't consider your feelings.

62
00:05:09,713 --> 00:05:10,792
You must be annoyed by me, right?

63
00:05:14,272 --> 00:05:16,913
Honestly, thank you.

64
00:05:17,512 --> 00:05:20,193
I didn't expect
you would actually send me off.

65
00:05:20,552 --> 00:05:21,633
I'm truly surprised.

66
