72
00:05:37,392 --> 00:05:39,112
I feel very happy anyway.

73
00:06:12,873 --> 00:06:13,873
Everyone, get out!

74
00:06:14,153 --> 00:06:15,873
Go back to your workstations. Hurry up.

75
