after you escaped once.

81
00:06:31,512 --> 00:06:33,392
You still have the guts
to play tricks with me?

82
00:06:35,352 --> 00:06:38,633
Do you really think
I don't dare to kill you?

83
00:06:38,873 --> 00:06:40,193
I don't understand what you're saying.

84
00:06:40,512 --> 00:06:41,313
Cut the crap!

85
00:06:41,873 --> 00:06:42,512
Hey, what are you doing?

86
00:06:43,552 --> 00:06:44,552
Shut up!

87
00:06:46,913 --> 00:06:47,392
What is it?

88
00:06:47,593 --> 00:06:48,272
I said shut up.

89
00:07:08,033 --> 00:07:09,193
Where's the thing you said?

90
00:07:10,672 --> 00:07:11,512
Search again.

91
00:07:11,993 --> 00:07:13,633
He really said it's on him.

92
00:07:13,913 --> 00:07:16,072
By the way, see if it's in his mouth.

93
00:07:16,753 --> 00:07:17,473
Zhang.

94
00:07:21,112 --> 00:07:22,112
Open your mouth.

95
00:07:34,352 --> 00:07:35,512
There's nothing in there.

96
00:07:36,072 --> 00:07:37,033
Are you messing with me?

97
00:07:38,232 --> 00:07:38,913
No, I'm not.

98
00:07:39,112 --> 00:07:41,913
I wouldn't dare to fool you
even if you let me.

99
00:07:42,433 --> 00:07:42,993
By the way,

100
00:07:43,672 --> 00:07:44,153
why don't...

101
00:07:44,672 --> 00:07:47,232
Maybe he swallowed it.

102
00:07:47,272 --> 00:07:47,993
Zhang, why you...

103
00:07:48,153 --> 00:07:50,112
Zhang, you were born to be a traitor.

104
00:07:51,792 --> 00:07:53,552
So it was in your stomach.

105
00:07:53,753 --> 00:07:56,193
Then I have to open you up
and take a look.

106
00:07:58,552 --> 00:07:59,352
I'll...

107
00:08:06,952 --> 00:08:08,593
Step back! I said step back!

108
00:08:09,232 --> 00:08:10,952
You want me to die, right?

109
00:08:10,952 --> 00:08:12,433
Today, no one will escape.

110
00:08:12,832 --> 00:08:13,313
Step back!

111
00:08:13,593 --> 00:08:14,112
Calm down.

112
00:08:15,153 --> 00:08:16,593
Xiaobei, don't do this!

113
00:08:16,913 --> 00:08:20,473
Xiaobei, I didn't mean to betray you.

114
00:08:23,153 --> 00:08:24,352
I have a wife
and children waiting for me

115
00:08:25,112 --> 00:08:27,552
to bring money back.

116
00:08:45,873 --> 00:08:46,273
Let me do it.

117
00:08:46,833 --> 00:08:47,393
It's okay.

118
00:08:48,513 --> 00:08:49,273
Thank you.

119
00:08:50,352 --> 00:08:50,633
Give it to me.

120
00:08:59,152 --> 00:09:02,352
My visit this time is quite abrupt.

121
00:09:02,433 --> 00:09:03,792
I've caused you a lot of trouble.

122
00:09:04,032 --> 00:09:04,633
Sorry about that.

123
00:09:05,672 --> 00:09:06,873
Well, I can't deny that.

124
00:09:07,472 --> 00:09:08,472
But I still want to thank you.

125
00:09:10,552 --> 00:09:11,112
For what?

126
00:09:12,712 --> 00:09:13,712
I'm really useless.

127
00:09:14,193 --> 00:09:15,313
I can't even express myself clearly.

128
00:09:19,393 --> 00:09:23,032
Xiao Mu'en,
we have a huge gap between us.

129
00:09:23,552 --> 00:09:25,513
I wanted to make things clear
when I returned home.

130
00:09:25,753 --> 00:09:27,712
But since things have come to this,

131
00:09:28,073 --> 00:09:29,712
I should tell you directly.

132
00:09:30,073 --> 00:09:30,953
We're not compatible.

133
00:09:42,433 --> 00:09:45,552
Are you officially rejecting me?

134
00:09:46,232 --> 00:09:46,792
Am I right?

135
00:09:50,712 --> 00:09:52,393
Don't be too serious.

136
00:09:53,193 --> 00:09:55,073
I think we're doing well as friends.

137
00:10:05,672 --> 00:10:06,433
I understand.

138
00:10:07,592 --> 00:10:08,112
Then...

139
00:10:09,953 --> 00:10:11,592
Then I wish your work
will go smoothly here

140
00:10:12,232 --> 00:10:12,993
and come home safely.

141
00:10:13,352 --> 00:10:14,953
You too, have a safe journey.

142
00:10:20,833 --> 00:10:22,112
