147
00:10:41,672 --> 00:10:43,273
Zhang Xiaobei,
you won't be able to escape!

148
00:10:43,313 --> 00:10:43,953
Step back!

149
00:10:44,273 --> 00:10:44,953
Don't come any closer!

150
00:10:45,352 --> 00:10:45,792
Get lost!

151
00:10:46,273 --> 00:10:46,672
Go away!

152
