Leave!

153
00:10:49,633 --> 00:10:51,032
- Stop right there!
- Stop!

154
00:10:51,592 --> 00:10:52,953
After him!

155
00:11:01,193 --> 00:11:01,953
Stop right there!

156
00:11:11,552 --> 00:11:13,152
You brat, where the hell did you go?

157
00:11:13,552 --> 00:11:14,953
Help me.

158
00:11:16,073 --> 00:11:16,633
Get in the car now!

159
00:11:17,712 --> 00:11:18,472
Stop right there!

160
00:11:20,993 --> 00:11:21,792
Stop!

161
00:11:22,873 --> 00:11:23,633
Stop!

162
00:11:28,472 --> 00:11:29,273
Don't be scared. It's the police.

163
00:11:29,552 --> 00:11:30,352
Madam, are you okay?

164
00:11:30,352 --> 00:11:31,352
Okay.

165
00:11:33,472 --> 00:11:33,833
You...

166
00:11:34,352 --> 00:11:35,472
You're injured.

167
00:11:35,753 --> 00:11:37,032
Let me check if you're hurt elsewhere.

168
00:11:37,152 --> 00:11:38,152
Are you hurt anywhere else?

169
00:11:39,592 --> 00:11:40,073
Help!

170
00:11:40,352 --> 00:11:41,592
We need help!

171
00:11:55,633 --> 00:11:57,352
Is this what you're looking for?

172
00:12:00,433 --> 00:12:01,112
Thank you very much.

173
00:12:01,152 --> 00:12:02,792
The surgery is over.

174
00:12:02,873 --> 00:12:04,552
You can visit him in a while.

175
00:12:04,712 --> 00:12:05,232
Okay.

176
00:12:11,472 --> 00:12:12,232
What is it, Han Xuan?

177
00:12:13,753 --> 00:12:14,552
Is An Ni hurt?

178
00:12:15,953 --> 00:12:16,712
Which hospital?

179
00:12:22,393 --> 00:12:23,032
Does it still hurt?

180
00:12:23,352 --> 00:12:24,273
It's okay.

181
00:12:28,552 --> 00:12:29,112
An Ni,

182
00:12:29,313 --> 00:12:29,912
are you okay?

183
00:12:30,193 --> 00:12:32,232
I'm fine. But Mr. Xiao is...

184
00:12:32,393 --> 00:12:33,232
I'm okay too.

185
00:12:33,592 --> 00:12:35,193
Just a few stitches on a flesh wound.

186
00:12:35,592 --> 00:12:36,993
I have to return to China today.

187
00:12:37,352 --> 00:12:38,273
It was too much.

188
00:12:38,672 --> 00:12:39,792
I'll report this to the superior now

189
00:12:39,873 --> 00:12:41,112
and ask them to coordinate
with the local police

190
00:12:41,152 --> 00:12:42,552
and provide us
with additional manpower to assist us.

191
00:12:43,592 --> 00:12:44,993
I'll send you to the airport later.

192
00:12:45,792 --> 00:12:46,672
Okay, thank you.

193
00:12:49,552 --> 00:12:52,393
This is a gift from Xiaobei.

194
00:13:14,633 --> 00:13:15,912
What can I do for you?

195
00:13:17,193 --> 00:13:17,993
Look at this.

196
00:13:21,152 --> 00:13:23,352
Our witness risked his life
to record this.

197
00:13:24,073 --> 00:13:26,712
So I'd like to ask
if the Gambling Commission

198
00:13:26,753 --> 00:13:27,912
can tolerate Qian Tianxin's
continued illegal activities.

199
00:13:28,433 --> 00:13:30,672
Apart from this,
I have bloodstains on my clothes too.

200
00:13:30,873 --> 00:13:32,513
There should be videos
of the shooting incident

201
00:13:32,552 --> 00:13:33,993
at the airport online.

202
00:13:34,032 --> 00:13:34,833
All of these are evidence

203
00:13:34,873 --> 00:13:36,232
of Qian Tianxin's crimes.

204
00:13:37,393 --> 00:13:41,552
She even dares to harm
the police in Country F,

205
00:13:42,032 --> 00:13:45,912
which led to the tragic death
of one officer and the injury of another.

206
00:13:46,753 --> 00:13:48,753
Therefore, the police department

207
00:13:48,792 --> 00:13:51,193
officially requests your cooperation

208
00:13:51,313 --> 00:13:53,592
to immediately assist the authorities
in investigating these crimes.

209
00:13:53,912 --> 00:13:55,792
We demand an immediate suspension

210
00:13:55,953 --> 00:14:00,193
of all gambling operations
by Qian Tianxin's company.

211
00:14:00,672 --> 00:14:01,273
Immediately.

212
00:14:02,273 --> 00:14:03,152
I said immediately.

213
00:14:06,073 --> 00:14:06,592
Very well.

214
00:14:12,152 --> 00:14:12,953
Hello?

215
00:14:14,592 --> 00:14:17,313
I regret to inform you that we've decided

216
00:14:17,352 --> 00:14:18,792
to suspend your business for today

217
00:14:19,672 --> 00:14:20,552
due to some activities

218
00:14:20,552 --> 00:14:22,833
that were against Country F.

219
00:14:23,193 --> 00:14:26,552
Moreover, if the company
was found performing illegally,

220
00:14:27,672 --> 00:14:30,152
we'll permanently
cancel your gambling license.

221
00:14:30,232 --> 00:14:31,552
Notice hereby given.

222
00:14:34,592 --> 00:14:35,073
All done.

223
00:14:35,513 --> 00:14:36,513
She's all yours now.

224
00:14:42,480 --> 00:14:47,912
(Jiangcheng People's Procuratorate
Remote Video Conference Room)

225
00:14:47,912 --> 00:14:49,032
I'm Guo Hongjiang.

226
00:14:50,112 --> 00:14:51,993
we'll immediately report this
to our superiors

227
00:14:52,513 --> 00:14:54,393
and contact the relevant authorities
in Country F,

228
00:14:54,993 --> 00:14:57,513
urging them to initiate
the arrest operation immediately.

229
00:14:58,633 --> 00:15:01,552
Comrades, be safe at all times.

230
00:15:02,352 --> 00:15:03,953
Obtain crucial evidence
as soon as possible.

231
00:15:06,073 --> 00:15:06,433
Okay.

232
00:15:07,393 --> 00:15:08,433
I wish everything will go smoothly.

233
00:15:34,592 --> 00:15:36,712
The mastermind
behind the killing of Officer Jose

234
00:15:36,753 --> 00:15:38,753
is Yang Wei, Qian Tianxin's subordinate.

235
00:15:39,232 --> 00:15:40,232
The time has come to seek justice

236
00:15:40,232 --> 00:15:41,753
for our fallen brother!

237
00:15:41,953 --> 00:15:43,912
We'll not allow criminals
to act lawlessly.

238
00:15:44,112 --> 00:15:45,433
Charge and arrest them!

239
00:15:45,472 --> 00:15:46,273
- Yes, sir!
- Yes, sir!

240
00:15:49,513 --> 00:15:50,352
Stay safe, everyone.

241
00:15:50,393 --> 00:15:50,953
Don't overstep your authority.

242
00:15:51,433 --> 00:15:51,912
- Yes, sir.
- Yes, sir.

243
00:15:52,313 --> 00:15:52,672
Keep up.

244
00:15:57,273 --> 00:15:57,912
Don't move!

245
00:15:58,112 --> 00:15:58,513
Freeze!

246
00:16:00,112 --> 00:16:00,753
Stand up!

247
00:16:01,393 --> 00:16:02,032
Don't move!

248
00:16:02,552 --> 00:16:03,193
Don't move!

249
00:16:04,953 --> 00:16:05,552
Stay still!

250
00:16:05,712 --> 00:16:06,152
I said stay still!

251
00:16:07,833 --> 00:16:08,352
Don't move!

252
00:16:09,352 --> 00:16:09,993
Stop!

253
00:16:10,633 --> 00:16:11,073
Don't move!

254
00:16:11,472 --> 00:16:11,993
Stay where you are!

255
00:16:15,032 --> 00:16:15,472
Move it!

256
00:16:26,352 --> 00:16:27,313
This isn't over yet.

257
00:16:28,472 --> 00:16:29,193
Just you wait.

258
00:16:29,552 --> 00:16:30,833
After we send you back home,

259
00:16:31,352 --> 00:16:32,993
I hope you can still speak
with confidence.

260
00:16:40,900 --> 00:16:42,820
(Income and Expenditure Statement)

261
00:17:39,232 --> 00:17:40,273
Han Xuan, where is it?

262
00:17:45,952 --> 00:17:47,273
Ni, this is the place
Zhang Xiaobei said.

263
00:17:47,952 --> 00:17:50,192
Gonzalez, the detained Chinese citizens
should be downstairs

264
00:17:50,312 --> 00:17:51,793
while the Chinese girls
who were deceived should be upstairs.

265
00:17:52,312 --> 00:17:54,072
I need one team to follow me
and search the upper floor.

266
00:17:54,112 --> 00:17:55,393
The other two teams will go downstairs.

267
00:17:55,513 --> 00:17:56,072
Be quick.

268
00:17:56,352 --> 00:17:56,913
Captain He,

269
00:17:56,952 --> 00:17:58,472
Do we need to use
the locksmith you asked me to find?

270
00:17:58,553 --> 00:17:59,112
Bring him here.

271
00:17:59,312 --> 00:17:59,753
Yes, sir.

272
00:18:00,112 --> 00:18:00,673
Stay safe!

273
00:18:10,592 --> 00:18:11,753
They didn't have time
to switch off the computers.

274
00:18:11,873 --> 00:18:12,913
They shouldn't be far.

275
